          "name": "E2E governance acceptance test",
          "criteria": "GOV-1: Full flow — spawn sandbox session, verify proxy URL in session env, verify MCP endpoint accessible with session token, verify tools/list returns granted tools only. GOV-2: Permission request surfaces via SSE stream. GOV-3: Proxy token record in DB is workspace-scoped and linked to correct identity. GOV-4: Agent session record has session_type=sandbox_agent.",
          "test_file": "tests/acceptance/sandbox-session-governance.test.ts",
          "scenario_name": "GOV-1, GOV-2, GOV-3, GOV-4"
        }
      ]
